Project location: Gorkha, Bhaktapur, Kalimati, Lalitpur, Lamjung, Sindhuli, Sindhupalchok
Project result:

 relief cargo delivered: 3 portable
 warehouses transported, 1,000
 tarpaulines transported, 20,000
 mosquito nets delivered, 4 Child
 Friendly space tents transported,
